title: Angle between Möbius spheres
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The hyperspheres corresponding to two points $$[s_1],[s_2]$$ outside $$\sphere^2$$ intersect at an angle $$\theta$$ determined by
$$
\cos\theta=
\frac
{\langle s_1,s_2\rangle_{3,1}}
{\sqrt{\langle s_1,s_1\rangle_{3,1}\langle s_2,s_2\rangle_{3,1}}}.
$$
This angle is determined up to $$\theta\leftrightarrow\pi-\theta.$$